    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a linear power band that remains a benchmark in naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a professional double-VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry is perfectly dialed, maintaining factory compliance with zero bushing deflection. Finished in a flawless Carbon Black Metallic over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this vehicle presents with zero mechanical or aesthetic defects. A turn-key performance icon that represents the pinnacle of the analog driving era.",
